Inez Palange https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Inez_Palange 0 Inez Palange (June 13, 1889 - October 16, 1962), also written as Ines Palange, was an Italian-born American actress who was best known for her role as Mrs. Camonte in the 1932 film Scarface.
